 better cater to user needs.=20
</p>

<p>
(<b>Please note that these wireframes primarily focus on navigation, layout=
, and content, rather than the User Interface (UI).</b>)
</p>

<p>
Your feedback is crucial at this stage, so please feel free to leave commen=
ts directly on Figma, via email, or let's schedule a quick
call to discuss. Thank you for taking part in this review.=20
